title: No Champions in Champselect
body:
Title: [8.17] - NO Champions in Champselect
Server: EUW
Type of Bug: Client
Details: I just started my laptop, started League, created a game of Nexusblitz, started queueing, got into Champselect but i couldnt pick and see any champions, i didn't even see the champs my teammates picked. After restarting the client the bug dissappeared.

replies.body: Den Bug hatte ich als der Client noch in der Testphase war, schön zu hören das es ihn immer noch gibt :D
